Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全身…都是樟腦的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從什麼時候開始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說點什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒打算做到這個地步的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本只是想將自己的一部分骨灰埋在這山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以拋去往事無所顧忌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在這裡打破了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是徹底成了邪魔外道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 從無法復生這點來說我本來就不算是人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 現在說什麼都晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種層面上都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點後知後覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這地方怎麼沒昆蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都要畫不是很麻煩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧 王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然把我當王子了？
